in response to some other posts about actually cracking it(otherwise it won't truly hide itself unless it is registered or cracked) you have to unhide the folder where it installs under 

C:\WINDOWS\system32\CTF

to unhide them on XP 
  1. open your hard drive (c:)
  2. at the top of the window go to tools.
  3. go to folder options.
  4. click on the tap "view"
  5. click on show hidden file types and folders

now you will be able to see the ctf folder.

also, when copying the serial.key file and the ctfmon.exe file make sure your program is not running (bottom right hand screen icon)
right click and close it, then copy the files and then click on the ctfmon.exe file that you just copies, it is now running again and set your options and hide it
(for god's sake don't click on register)

~thanks multii~
